<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bareness" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bareness,</orth> 1) nakedness: <cit><quote>beauty o'ersnowed and b. everywhere,</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 5.8" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 5, 8</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>old December's b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 2.97.4" default="NO" valid="yes">97, 4</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.2.20" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 2, 20</bibl>.<lb />2) leanness: <cit><quote>for their b., I am sure they never learned that of me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 4.2.77" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A IV, 2, 77</bibl></cit>.
